<p class="">The conference is an exploratory one, and the matters upon which views will be exchanged affect in the main the three Governments taking part. We have informed the French Government that we shall not commit ourselves in Moscow on matters of concern to France in her absence.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
